com.kissair.dao

  • Packages that use com.kissair.dao 
    Package Description
    com.kissair.dao
    This package contains interfaces of Data Access Objects and a factory class for creating the latter.
    com.kissair.dao.hibernate
    This package provides implementations of Data Access Objects for using with Hibernate.
    com.kissair.dao.jdbc
    This package provides implementations of Data Access Objects for using with the JDBC.
